@startuml
left to right direction
title Diagrama de contexto

actor "Ingeniero de QA" as QA

rectangle "Sistema" as SISTEMA
rectangle "Modelo de IA\n(OpenAI)" as MODELO
rectangle "Kiwi TCMS\nSistema externo" as KIWI

QA --> SISTEMA 
QA --> KIWI
MODELO --> SISTEMA
SISTEMA --> MODELO : Consume modelo
SISTEMA --> KIWI 
KIWI --> SISTEMA 
@enduml